import { useContext, useRef } from "react"; import { ApiContext } from "../../context/ApiContext"; import axios from "axios"; const MessageModal = () => { const {messageID, messageName,} = useContext(ApiContext) const title = useRef(); const description = useRef(); const handleOnSubmit = async(e) => { e.preventDefault(); const dataBody = new FormData(); dataBody.append('title', title); dataBody.append('description', description); dataBody.append("messageID", messageID); dataBody.append("nameOfMessage", messageName); await axios.post("send/add", dataBody, { header: { Authorization: "Bearer " + localStorage.getItem("access_token"), } }).then((response)=> { if (response.data.success) { console.log("oldi lan") } }).catch((error)=>{ console.log(error) }) } return (
